<p>如果沒有報錯, 代表安裝成功。</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">gaps inner 20
gaps outer 20

for_window <span class="o">[</span><span class="nv">class</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"^.*"</span><span class="o">]</span> border pixel 10

smart_borders on
smart_borders no_gaps
